        {"speaker": "B", "roman": "baavi mattu kaalve madhyadallittu.", "english": "It was inbetween the well and the canal."},
        {"speaker": "A", "roman": "sari, adanna tagolli, beeg banni, hottaaytu.", "english": "Yes, take it, come quickly. It is getting late."}
